snippet.title: Stargate SG-1: Unleashed Game Play Trailer
snippet.description:
http://bit.ly/18pj2CZ Try now for free the LITE version of Stargate SG-1: Unleashed Ep1 for iOS

http://bit.ly/16KZWYI Download from here the LITE version for Google Play Store for free!

Get a preview of the game-play experience with this trailer for the upcoming interactive adventure, Stargate SG-1: Unleashed.  You get to be the SG-1 team, not just one character, but actually play as O'Neill, Carter and Jackson in a totally new engaging story based on the original Stargate SG-1 TV series. FOR MORE INFO: http://www.arkalisinteractive.com/stargate-sg-1-unleashed/
